Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:00.14,0:06:01.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}三號機和四號機
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:01.66,0:06:05.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}不都是他們號稱享有建造權於是硬搶過去造的嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:05.10,0:06:07.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}事到如今竟然把危險推給我們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:07.92,0:06:09.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}實在太自私了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:09.46,0:06:12.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}經過那種慘劇之後，任誰都會退縮的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:13.05,0:06:14.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}那麼，啟動試驗怎么辦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:15.23,0:06:16.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}要用那個傀儡系統嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:17.51,0:06:18.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}已經決定了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:21.26,0:06:22.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}這是試驗型的傀儡系統
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:23.45,0:06:25.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}裡面移植了零的個人資料
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:25.73,0:06:28.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}可是，人的心、靈魂無法數位化
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:29.70,0:06:31.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}充其量這只是虛假的、模擬的東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:32.47,0:06:35.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}只是模仿駕駛員思考的機器
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:36.19,0:06:38.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}把信號模式送進{\rED} EVA
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:38.93,0:06:42.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}只要{\rED} EVA {\r}認為有駕駛員在，能夠進行同步就行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:43.46,0:06:45.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}開始向初號機和二號機輸入數據
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:46.36,0:06:48.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}但是還存在一些問題
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:48.48,0:06:49.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}沒關係
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:49.48,0:06:50.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}只要{\rED} EVA {\r}能動就行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:51.09,0:06:51.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:54.64,0:06:57.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}機體的搬運由{\rED} UN {\r}全權負責
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:57.77,0:06:59.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}周末應該可以運到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:00.06,0:07:01.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}接下來就由妳那裡負責
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:02.19,0:07:02.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:03.24,0:07:06.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}調整和啟動試驗將在松代進行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:06.68,0:07:07.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}測試駕駛員呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:08.04,0:07:09.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}傀儡插入栓還有危險
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:10.08,0:07:11.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}我想從現有的候補人員裡面…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:11.78,0:07:13.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}選出第四個嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:13.57,0:07:13.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:14.54,0:07:17.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}有個孩子能夠很快進行「核」的準備
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:18.24,0:07:18.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}拜託了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:19.36,0:07:19.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:21.65,0:07:23.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}零，可以上來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:24.67,0:07:25.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:25.53,0:07:26.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}陪我吃飯吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:27.05,0:07:27.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:35.20,0:07:35.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}起立
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:36.50,0:07:36.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}敬禮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:38.18,0:07:40.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}吃飯嘍、吃飯嘍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:40.31,0:07:42.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}這可是在學校最大的樂趣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:42.66,0:07:44.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}哎——
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:45.85,0:07:47.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}你沒有帶便當來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:47.99,0:07:51.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}昨…昨天要趕作業沒時間做啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:51.23,0:07:55.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}因為這點小事你就要本小姐沒午飯吃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:56.03,0:07:58.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}什麼嘛，小倆口又吵架啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:02.87,0:08:03.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}才不是呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:05.56,0:08:06.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}什麼事情這麼鄭重
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:08.01,0:08:10.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}在松代的三號機啟動實驗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:10.71,0:08:12.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}測試駕駛員將啟用第{\rED} 4 {\r}個人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:13.11,0:08:13.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}第{\rED} 4 {\r}個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:14.34,0:08:15.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}找到第四適格者了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:16.83,0:08:17.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}就在昨天
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:18.49,0:08:20.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}我沒有收到馬爾杜克機關的報告
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:21.45,0:08:23.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}正式文件明天會到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:26.82,0:08:27.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}赤木博士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:28.32,0:08:30.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}妳是不是又有什麼事情瞞著我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:30.80,0:08:31.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}沒有啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:32.11,0:08:33.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}算了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:33.42,0:08:35.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}那個被選出來的孩子是誰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:41.51,0:08:43.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}為什麼偏偏是這個孩子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:43.99,0:08:44.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}沒辦法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:45.47,0:08:47.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}因為候補人員是集中保護的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:47.98,0:08:49.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}這件事很難開口
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:50.58,0:08:51.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}明日香還好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:51.80,0:08:53.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}駕駛{\rED} EVA {\r}就是她的驕傲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:54.40,0:08:55.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}而零是例外
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:56.82,0:08:59.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}跟我們及{\rED} EVA {\r}扯上關系後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:00.62,0:09:02.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}就沒什麼好事
