Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:21.94,0:09:22.94,BGS,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a3}啊～累死了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:24.92,0:09:28.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}鈴原，今天輪到你做值日生，要認真做
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:28.68,0:09:29.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}什麼事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:29.76,0:09:30.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}講義
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:31.56,0:09:33.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}老師不是叫你送過去嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:34.11,0:09:35.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}幹嘛這樣～班長大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:35.40,0:09:36.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}讓另一個值日生做嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:37.29,0:09:38.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}綾波同學今天請假
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:39.39,0:09:40.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}本周值日是綾波和我啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:41.43,0:09:42.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}那就沒辦法了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:43.69,0:09:46.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}可是一個人去女孩子家怪怪的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:46.24,0:09:48.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}那就讓我陪你一起…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:48.27,0:09:48.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}真嗣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:50.15,0:09:51.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}陪我一起去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:15.18,0:10:15.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}綾波
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:16.75,0:10:17.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}我們要進去啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:17.94,0:10:20.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}擅自進入女孩子的房間我覺得不太好啊
