Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:22.42,0:10:24.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}就算放進這裡她也不會看到的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:27.59,0:10:28.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}打擾了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:38.08,0:10:39.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}什麼嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:39.90,0:10:41.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}這真的是女孩子的房間嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:42.25,0:10:43.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}不敢恭維啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:59.87,0:11:00.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}幹什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:00.68,0:11:02.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}亂動會挨罵喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:02.77,0:11:04.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}我只是整理一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:05.74,0:11:07.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}我可不會幫忙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:07.84,0:11:08.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}這不是男人該做的事情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:09.48,0:11:12.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}不過，你這樣會被美里討厭喔
