Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:16.16,0:11:17.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}因為這是我的信念
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:22.71,0:11:25.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}真的變了好多
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:26.04,0:11:26.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:27.04,0:11:28.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}真嗣啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:31.20,0:11:32.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}老實說第一次見面時
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:32.86,0:11:34.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}我覺得你是個討厭的家伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:35.92,0:11:38.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}我也不認為你會替別人做什麼
