Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:54.91,0:11:55.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}什麼事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:55.91,0:11:57.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}那是累積下來的講義
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:02.83,0:12:03.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:04.46,0:12:05.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}我擅自整理了一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:06.15,0:12:07.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}除了垃圾其它都沒碰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:10.55,0:12:12.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}謝…謝謝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:16.93,0:12:17.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}說真的
