Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:09.57,0:13:11.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}為了滿足自己的快樂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:12.38,0:13:14.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}而自己創造的樂園嗎
